520
00:37:43,700 --> 00:37:45,600
<i>[Qing Ji: A Blue Feather Phoenix]</i>

521
00:37:51,480 --> 00:37:52,780
Master Qing.

522
00:37:52,780 --> 00:37:56,360
Little Li Shu, you saved me with your life?

523
00:37:56,360 --> 00:37:58,240
Li Shu was late...

524
